OL,5, Businesses will close if a tourism tax 
OL,6, is introduced in Wales, according to   
OL,7, industry leaders.                      
OL,9,FThe Wales Tourism Alliance (WTA) said  
OL,10,Fmany feared the tax would lead to less 
OL,11,Fvisitors as businesses struggled to    
OL,12,Fcope with rising energy bills.         
OL,14,FThe Welsh government said tourism      
OL,15,Flevies were common across the world and
OL,16,Fcould improve local services.          
OL,18,FBut one operator said Wales would be in
OL,19,F"big trouble" if it became the only    
OL,20,Fdevolved nation to adopt such a tax.   
